Plan Your Event
Plean Your Event at
orlandogolfclubrentalstogo.com
Travel Agents/Event Organizers
Renting from
OrlandoGolfClubRentalsToGo.com
makes planning a round of golf for your clients easy. With a 24-hour notice we can deliver sets of clubs to your customers at their Orlando area hotel, or the course they have chosen to play some golf. Renting from us gives your clients usage of newest golf equipment from the No. 1 golf club company, Callaway Golf.
OrlandoGolfClubRentalsToGo.com
has sets for players of all skills levels. We have sets for beginners, intermediate and advance golfers. Check out our Available Sets section on this site to see what we have to offer.
If you need help determine which sets are best to rent please call us or send an email to discuss what is right for your customers.
In addition, if you need advice on where they should play we can do that too. We have been Central Florida residents for nearly 30 years.
Call :
407-230-0734
Email :
[email protected]
What you can expect
The best pricing on complete rentals sets from the great Callaway Golf. Sets start at
$110
per 2 days.
Outstanding customer service. We will personally deliver the clubs to your clients at their hotel in Central Florida and pick them up when completed.
Choose from :
Men’s Right handed or Left handed sets and Ladies too.
Rent the desired sets from here

About orlando Golfclub Rentalstogo
OrlandoGolfClubRentalsToGo is Central Florida’s leader in golf club rental sets. We possess over 25 years of retail golf experience, and pride ourselves on outstanding customer service. Offering Callaway Golf clubs for rent makes us the top rental destination in the Orlando market. Delivering your rental set to your hotel or golf course will make playing a round of golf stress free, and most importantly a great day on the links!
OrlandoGolfClubRentalsToGo is an extension of the website GolfersTrunk.com. This site is owned and operated by John Maloney a 23-year veteran of the Edwin Watts Golf chain of golf stores. He has established himself as one of Central Florida’s premier golf club fitters for players of all skills levels.
